<h2>Before Your First Session</h2>
<p>Before your first treatment, we will ask you to complete a short intake questionnaire covering your health history, current symptoms and any specific concerns. This helps us personalise your four-hands treatment from the very first session.</p>
<p>Please wear comfortable, loose-fitting clothing. Sessions typically last 90 to 120 minutes. We recommend arriving a few minutes early to settle in.</p>
